{
  "stem": "5891.4",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This is stupid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They're going to explode me here?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They won't do that, because they're going to explode them self.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So right after that, they took one box off.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So now I'm hanging there a little bit, but I'm still touching a little bit.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Now they took off the other box.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Yeah, I don't think you ever hung on your arms, did you?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You're not on the floor, and you're not on the, on the end.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You know, you're hanging.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You're not really, but you're not on the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So I don't know how long I hung there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Quite a while.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Oh, terrible.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Hours?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Terrible.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Terrible.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I finally-- when I hadn't came to again, you know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they finally came and took me down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And almost like there was something wrong here, with my, my shoulders.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they took, brought me back to the barracks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The next-- I thought now I was through with them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, the next night, when this appel, that the whole camp has to come out-- Block 5, Block 6, Block 8, whatever their numbers were there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And every block kapo has to count the people and then give-- call in the report.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they'd march by there and you'd give them the reports.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And after the report is done, if there's any kind of a remarks to be made, the commander does it right then and there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now, what they were doing, they were bringing one of those square tables, just a square pit, just a ordinary square bench, a work, a little work bench, where men, men work at, but a little lower.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it, it's, it's crossed like this on each side.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There's enough room.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, anyway, they called my number out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, oh, god.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
